started doing it again and the whole country

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:17.639
got involved. I have another good story that
I want share with you. Abolition and the anti-slavery

00:18:17.639 --> 00:18:22.740
was started early in Massachusetts. And I
think sometimes people think Boston is very

00:18:22.740 --> 00:18:27.700
racist. We get that kind of a bad rap about
